k8s starts with four initial namespaces
1.Default
2.kube-node-release
3.kube-public
4.kube-system
To check the namespaces
#kubectl get namespaces (ns) shortcut
To create a namespaces
#kubectl create ns <namespace name> eg: development
To switch the namespaces
#kubectl config set-context --current --namespace=development
#kubectl config set-context --current --namespace=default
To list all the pods ,nodes,namespace,labels
#kubectl get all -A
To delete the namespace
#kubectl delete ns <ns name>  eg:development
To delet the pods
#kubectl delete pods <names of all pods>
